(ns farsund.data.query
  (:require [com.rpl.specter :as sp]
            [cuerdas.core :as str]))


(defn select-product [key val data]
  (sp/select-one [sp/ALL #(= val (get % key))] data))


(defn order->market-order [order categories min-pace min-margin]
  (into []
    (comp
      (filter #(contains? (set categories) (subs (:category-id %) 0 2)))
      (filter #(> (:pace %) min-pace))
      (filter #(> (:margin %) min-margin))
      (filter #(not (str/starts-with? (:id %) "F")))
      (filter #(or (not (:cg-price %))
                   (<= (* (:purchase-price %) 1.05) (:cg-price %)))))
    order))


(defn order->cg-order [order categories min-pace min-margin]
  (into []
    (comp
      (filter #(contains? (set categories) (subs (:category-id %) 0 2)))
      (filter #(str/empty-or-nil? (:promotion %)))
      (filter #(> (:pace %) min-pace))
      (filter #(> (:margin %) min-margin))
      (filter #(pos? (:cg-stock %)))
      (filter #(or (not (:purchase-price %)) (> (* (:purchase-price %) 1.05) (:cg-price %)))))
    order))
